    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Male genitalia of Siberian Sterrhinae. A, B—Idaea sylvestraria; C–E—I. pallidata; F, G—I. nitidata; H, I—I. biselata; J, K—I. aversata; L, M—I. straminata. A, C—genital segment, lateral view; D—ditto, ventral view, valvae shifted; F, H, J, L—ditto, ventral view; B, E, G, I, K, M—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
